#: admin/views/settings.php:14
msgid "Banner Control"
msgstr "Contrôle de la bannière"

#: admin/views/settings.php:21
msgid "Enable cookie banner"
msgstr "Activer la bannière cookie"

#: admin/views/settings.php:23
msgid ""
"When disabled, the cookie consent banner will not appear on your site and no "
"scripts will be blocked."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque désactivé, la bannière de consentement aux cookies n'apparaîtra pas "
"sur votre site et aucun script ne sera bloqué."

#: admin/views/settings.php:26
msgid "Excluded Pages"
msgstr "Pages exclues"

#: admin/views/settings.php:27
msgid "One per line: page ID or URL pattern like /privacy/*"
msgstr "Un par ligne : ID de page ou modèle d'URL comme /privacy/*"

#: admin/views/settings.php:28
msgid "Enter page IDs or URL patterns, one per line."
msgstr "Saisissez les ID de page ou les modèles d'URL, un par ligne."

#: admin/views/settings.php:34
msgid "Hide banner from search engine bots"
msgstr "Masquer la bannière aux robots des moteurs de recherche"

#: admin/views/settings.php:36
msgid ""
"Automatically detects search engine crawlers (Googlebot, Bingbot, etc.) and "
"skips the banner for them. Improves SEO by serving cleaner HTML to crawlers."
msgstr ""
"Détecte automatiquement les robots des moteurs de recherche (Googlebot, "
"Bingbot, etc.) et ne leur affiche pas la bannière. Améliore le SEO en "
"servant un HTML plus propre aux robots."

#: admin/views/settings.php:42
msgid "Push consent events to GTM Data Layer"
msgstr "Envoyer les événements de consentement au GTM Data Layer"

#: admin/views/settings.php:44
msgid ""
"Pushes a faz_consent_update event with per-category granted/denied values to "
"window.dataLayer after each consent action. Enable if you use Google Tag "
"Manager."
msgstr ""
"Envoie un événement faz_consent_update avec les valeurs accordé/refusé par "
"catégorie vers window.dataLayer après chaque action de consentement. Activez "
"si vous utilisez Google Tag Manager."

#: admin/views/settings.php:50
msgid "Ad-blocker compatibility mode"
msgstr "Mode de compatibilité anti-bloqueurs de publicité"

#: admin/views/settings.php:52
msgid ""
"Uses generic script handle names to prevent ad blockers from blocking the "
"cookie banner. Enable if visitors report the banner not appearing."
msgstr ""
"Utilise des noms de handle de script génériques pour empêcher les bloqueurs "
"de publicité de bloquer la bannière cookie. Activez si des visiteurs "
"signalent que la bannière n'apparaît pas."

#: admin/views/settings.php:58
msgid "Enable per-service consent"
msgstr "Activer le consentement par service"

#: admin/views/settings.php:60
msgid ""
"When enabled, visitors can accept or reject individual services (e.g., "
"Google Analytics, YouTube) instead of entire categories. This provides more "
"granular privacy control but makes the preference center more complex."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque activé, les visiteurs peuvent accepter ou refuser des services "
"individuels (par ex. Google Analytics, YouTube) au lieu de catégories "
"entières. Cela offre un contrôle de la vie privée plus granulaire mais rend "
"le centre de préférences plus complexe."

#: admin/views/settings.php:67 admin/views/system-status.php:81
msgid "Cross-Domain Consent"
msgstr "Consentement inter-domaines"

#: admin/views/settings.php:74
msgid "Enable cross-domain consent forwarding"
msgstr "Activer le transfert de consentement inter-domaines"

#: admin/views/settings.php:76
msgid ""
"Share consent choices across multiple domains. When a visitor accepts or "
"rejects cookies on one domain, the same choice is forwarded to all "
"configured target domains via secure postMessage."
msgstr ""
"Partagez les choix de consentement entre plusieurs domaines. Lorsqu'un "
"visiteur accepte ou refuse les cookies sur un domaine, le même choix est "
"transmis à tous les domaines cibles configurés via postMessage sécurisé."

#: admin/views/settings.php:79
msgid "Target Domains"
msgstr "Domaines cibles"

#: admin/views/settings.php:80
msgid "One per line: https://shop.example.com"
msgstr "Un par ligne : https://shop.example.com"

#: admin/views/settings.php:81
msgid ""
"Full URLs of other sites that should receive consent state. Each site must "
"also have FAZ Cookie Manager installed. One URL per line."
msgstr ""
"URL complètes des autres sites qui doivent recevoir l'état du consentement. "
"Chaque site doit également avoir FAZ Cookie Manager installé. Une URL par "
"ligne."

#: admin/views/settings.php:88 admin/views/system-status.php:74
msgid "Pageview Tracking"
msgstr "Suivi des pages vues"

#: admin/views/settings.php:95
msgid "Enable pageview and banner interaction tracking"
msgstr "Activer le suivi des pages vues et des interactions avec la bannière"

#: admin/views/settings.php:97
msgid ""
"Tracks pageviews and banner interactions (accept, reject, settings) for the "
"dashboard analytics. This sends first-party data (page URL, title, session "
"ID) before consent is given. Disable for stricter compliance."
msgstr ""
"Suit les pages vues et les interactions avec la bannière (accepter, refuser, "
"paramètres) pour les analyses du tableau de bord. Cela envoie des données "
"first-party (URL de la page, titre, ID de session) avant que le "
"consentement ne soit donné. Désactivez pour une conformité plus stricte."

#: admin/views/settings.php:104
msgid "Script Blocking"
msgstr "Blocage de scripts"

#: admin/views/settings.php:108
msgid "Pages Excluded from Script Blocking"
msgstr "Pages exclues du blocage de scripts"

#: admin/views/settings.php:109
msgid "One per line: /checkout/* or /cart/*"
msgstr "Un par ligne : /checkout/* ou /cart/*"

#: admin/views/settings.php:110
msgid ""
"URL patterns where script blocking is disabled (banner still shows). One per "
"line, supports wildcards (e.g. <code>/checkout/*</code>)."
msgstr ""
"Modèles d'URL où le blocage de scripts est désactivé (la bannière reste "
"visible). Un par ligne, supporte les caractères génériques (par ex. "
"<code>/checkout/*</code>)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:124
msgid "Enable consent logging"
msgstr "Activer la journalisation du consentement"

#: admin/views/settings.php:126
msgid ""
"Records each visitor's consent choice (accepted, rejected, or partial) for "
"GDPR accountability. Required by Art. 7(1) GDPR to demonstrate that consent "
"was given."
msgstr ""
"Enregistre le choix de consentement de chaque visiteur (accepté, refusé ou "
"partiel) pour la responsabilité GDPR. Requis par l'art. 7(1) du GDPR pour "
"démontrer que le consentement a été donné."

#: admin/views/settings.php:129
msgid "Retention Period (months)"
msgstr "Période de conservation (mois)"

#: admin/views/settings.php:131
msgid ""
"How long consent records are kept before automatic deletion. Most DPAs "
"recommend 12 months. Logs older than this period are purged daily."
msgstr ""
"Durée de conservation des enregistrements de consentement avant suppression "
"automatique. La plupart des autorités de protection des données recommandent "
"12 mois. Les journaux antérieurs à cette période sont purgés quotidiennement."

#: admin/views/settings.php:138
msgid "Scanner"
msgstr "Scanner"

#: admin/views/settings.php:142
msgid "Max Pages to Scan"
msgstr "Nombre max. de pages à analyser"

#: admin/views/settings.php:144
msgid ""
"Maximum number of pages the cookie scanner will crawl. Higher values find "
"more cookies but take longer. 100 pages is sufficient for most sites."
msgstr ""
"Nombre maximum de pages que le scanner de cookies va parcourir. Des valeurs "
"plus élevées trouvent plus de cookies mais prennent plus de temps. 100 pages "
"suffisent pour la plupart des sites."

#: admin/views/settings.php:151
msgid "Automatic Scanning"
msgstr "Analyse automatique"

#: admin/views/settings.php:158
msgid "Enable automatic cookie scanning"
msgstr "Activer l'analyse automatique des cookies"

#: admin/views/settings.php:160
msgid ""
"Automatically scan your site for new cookies on a schedule. You will receive "
"an email notification if new uncategorized cookies are found."
msgstr ""
"Analyse automatiquement votre site à la recherche de nouveaux cookies selon "
"un calendrier. Vous recevrez une notification par e-mail si de nouveaux "
"cookies non catégorisés sont trouvés."

#: admin/views/settings.php:163
msgid "Scan Frequency"
msgstr "Fréquence d'analyse"

#: admin/views/settings.php:165
msgid "Daily"
msgstr "Quotidienne"

#: admin/views/settings.php:166 includes/class-activator.php:107
msgid "Weekly"
msgstr "Hebdomadaire"

#: admin/views/settings.php:167
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "Mensuelle"

#: admin/views/settings.php:169
msgid ""
"How often the scanner runs automatically. Weekly is recommended for most "
"sites."
msgstr ""
"Fréquence d'exécution automatique du scanner. Hebdomadaire est recommandé "
"pour la plupart des sites."

#: admin/views/settings.php:176
msgid "Microsoft Consent APIs"
msgstr "API de consentement Microsoft"

#: admin/views/settings.php:183
msgid "Microsoft UET Consent Mode"
msgstr "Microsoft UET Consent Mode"

#: admin/views/settings.php:185
msgid ""
"Signals consent status to Microsoft Advertising (Bing Ads) via the UET tag. "
"Enable if you use Microsoft Advertising and need to respect consent for ad "
"tracking."
msgstr ""
"Signale l'état du consentement à Microsoft Advertising (Bing Ads) via la "
"balise UET. Activez si vous utilisez Microsoft Advertising et devez "
"respecter le consentement pour le suivi publicitaire."

#: admin/views/settings.php:191
msgid "Microsoft Clarity Consent API"
msgstr "API de consentement Microsoft Clarity"

#: admin/views/settings.php:193
msgid ""
"Signals consent status to Microsoft Clarity (heatmaps and session "
"recordings). Enable if you use Clarity and want it to pause tracking until "
"consent is given."
msgstr ""
"Signale l'état du consentement à Microsoft Clarity (cartes de chaleur et "
"enregistrements de session). Activez si vous utilisez Clarity et souhaitez "
"qu'il suspende le suivi jusqu'à ce que le consentement soit donné."

#: admin/views/settings.php:200
msgid "Age Verification"
msgstr "Vérification de l'âge"

#: admin/views/settings.php:207
msgid "Require age verification for consent"
msgstr "Exiger la vérification de l'âge pour le consentement"

#: admin/views/settings.php:209
msgid ""
"Under GDPR Art. 8, children below the minimum age cannot give valid consent "
"for data processing. When enabled, visitors must confirm they meet the "
"minimum age before accepting optional cookies."
msgstr ""
"En vertu de l'art. 8 du GDPR, les enfants n'ayant pas atteint l'âge minimum "
"ne peuvent pas donner un consentement valide pour le traitement des données. "
"Lorsque activé, les visiteurs doivent confirmer qu'ils ont l'âge minimum "
"requis avant d'accepter les cookies optionnels."

#: admin/views/settings.php:212
msgid "Minimum Age"
msgstr "Âge minimum"

#: admin/views/settings.php:214
msgid ""
"GDPR default is 16. Some EU member states allow 13-15. Check your local law."
msgstr ""
"La valeur par défaut du GDPR est 16 ans. Certains États membres de l'UE "
"autorisent 13-15 ans. Vérifiez votre législation locale."

#: admin/views/settings.php:221
msgid "IAB TCF"
msgstr "IAB TCF"

#: admin/views/settings.php:228
msgid "Enable IAB TCF v2.3"
msgstr "Activer IAB TCF v2.3"

#: admin/views/settings.php:230
msgid ""
"Enables the IAB Transparency & Consent Framework. Required if you work with "
"ad-tech vendors that need a standardised TC String for programmatic "
"advertising in the EU."
msgstr ""
"Active le cadre de transparence et de consentement IAB. Requis si vous "
"travaillez avec des fournisseurs ad-tech qui ont besoin d'une chaîne TC "
"standardisée pour la publicité programmatique dans l'UE."

#: admin/views/settings.php:233
msgid "Publisher Country Code"
msgstr "Code pays de l'éditeur"

#: admin/views/settings.php:235
msgid ""
"ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 code of the publisher's country (e.g. IT, DE, FR). Used "
"in the TCF consent string."
msgstr ""
"Code ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 du pays de l'éditeur (par ex. IT, DE, FR). Utilisé "
"dans la chaîne de consentement TCF."

#: admin/views/settings.php:238
msgid "CMP ID"
msgstr "ID CMP"

#: admin/views/settings.php:240
msgid ""
"Your registered IAB CMP ID (<a href=\"https://iabeurope.eu/cmp-list/\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IAB CMP List</a>). With "
"ID&nbsp;0 the banner and cookie blocking work normally, but ad-tech vendors "
"will ignore the TC String. Google Consent Mode v2 works regardless of CMP "
"registration."
msgstr ""
"Votre ID CMP IAB enregistré (<a href=\"https://iabeurope.eu/cmp-list/\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Liste des CMP IAB</a>). Avec "
"l'ID&nbsp;0, la bannière et le blocage de cookies fonctionnent normalement, "
"mais les fournisseurs ad-tech ignoreront la chaîne TC. Google Consent "
"Mode v2 fonctionne indépendamment de l'enregistrement CMP."

#: admin/views/settings.php:246
msgid "Purpose One Treatment"
msgstr "Traitement du Purpose One"

#: admin/views/settings.php:248
msgid ""
"Set to true if Purpose 1 consent was NOT disclosed (e.g. publisher in a "
"country where Purpose 1 is not required)."
msgstr ""
"Définir sur true si le consentement au Purpose 1 n'a PAS été divulgué (par "
"ex. éditeur dans un pays où le Purpose 1 n'est pas requis)."

#: admin/views/settings.php:252
msgid "Loading GVL status..."
msgstr "Chargement de l'état de la GVL..."

#: admin/views/settings.php:254
msgid "Update GVL Now"
msgstr "Mettre à jour la GVL maintenant"

